  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Your Opportunity As Real Train Mechanic.</h2>Find locomotives around the game world that needs your help and repair them in one of 3 workshops localized in huge 25 km2 open world. <br>You will face all types of damages in all genres of trains: Diesel, Electric and even Old-School Steam units.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><li> 9 trains to repair in all types: Steam, Electric and Diesel<br></li><li> open 25 km2 world full of railways and different locations<br></li><li> 3 workshops with more than 1000 parts to repair<br></li><li> unique Economy System – you will decide about strategy of repair and ROI of it</li></ul>[/h2]<br>[/list]",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Your Opportunity As Real Train Mechanic.</h2>Find locomotives around the game world that needs your help and repair them in one of 3 workshops localized in huge 25 km2 open world. <br>You will face all types of damages in all genres of trains: Diesel, Electric and even Old-School Steam units.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><li> 9 trains to repair in all types: Steam, Electric and Diesel<br></li><li> open 25 km2 world full of railways and different locations<br></li><li> 3 workshops with more than 1000 parts to repair<br></li><li> unique Economy System – you will decide about strategy of repair and ROI of it</li></ul>[/h2]<br>[/list]",
